{%- comment -%}
Technical head holds all 'General / Global' assets / dependencies refererenced 
within <head> such as scripts, CSS, font references, favicons, Insites dependencies, etc. 
(Insites assets, GTM, etc..)

We try to limit assets that are part of the technical head to minimize page size 
& improve page performance.

Assets like 'Google Map API', should only be referenced as needed.
- Managed on the 'page / layout' level
{%- endcomment -%}
{% liquid
    include 'modules/website/layout/technical-head/google-fonts'
    include 'modules/website/layout/technical-head/favicons'
    include 'modules/website/layout/technical-head/msapplication'
    include 'modules/website/layout/technical-head/vendor-assets'
    include 'modules/website/layout/technical-head/insites-assets'
    include 'modules/website/layout/project_assets'
%}

